## Grafana Dashboard (Kubernetes Monitoring)

Grafana Dashboard Link: [View Dashboard](http://localhost:3000/public-dashboards/1f2b674b154b4863b5750fdf18b33dd3)

This dashboard visualizes:

- Application request metrics  
- Pod CPU and memory usage  
- Cluster resource utilization  
- Alerts triggered by Prometheus rules

> ⚠️ **Note:** This link works when Grafana is running locally on your machine.

